      "content": "i get that but i've already tried talking to my dr and they just told me to \"give it time\" which is so frustrating... i've been on it for weeks and the nausea isn't going away. i really feel like i know my own body better than a doctor who only sees me for 10 mins. if i just taper off the sertraline slowly over a week and start the st johns wort, would that be a safer way to do it? i just want to feel normal again without all the heavy drugs.",
